Products and Services for Any Project












PRODUCTS AND SERVICES 




Tools, Technology, Equipment and Expertise
From proprietary technologies to the everyday tools and services that help drive the nation's energy industry, bringing KLX Energy Services into your project from the start better prepares your operation to avoid Non-Productive Time (NPT) throughout the life of the asset.












Surface Facilities & Equipment 


Put the basics in place with greater confidence and convenience, whether you need accommodations, utilities, cranes, lighting or more.











Pressure Control Services 


Get total pressure control coverage including BOPs, frac stacks and our proprietary KLX Frac Relief Valve System.











Wireline Services 


Deploy state-of-the-art electric and slickline units, and experienced crews, for logging, setting, perforation, pump-down and more.











Fishing Services 


Let our experienced fishing specialists, and one of the largest selections of fishing tools in the industry, get you back on track.











Downhole Technology & Tools 


Access 50+ downhole products to support any phase of operation, from downhole essentials to new KLX Energy Services innovations.











Thru Tubing Solutions 


Access a wide range of thru-tubing tools and technologies, as well as specialized experts who help you make the most of them.











Engineered Products 


Optimize the efficiency of field service operations with innovative new technologies designed in-house and available exclusively at KLX Energy Services.







































